{"id":232922790,"title":"承諾離開的時候總是很安靜","content":"他們一個個地走了\n離開之前\n還不忘貼心的關上門\n深怕我懶得起身\n\n燈也一併關上吧\n免得太過刺眼\n我也不會以為\n還有人在\n\n才能安心入睡吧\n雖然不知道\n明早會不會醒來\n不過那都沒關係了\n\n承諾離開的時候總是很安靜\n震耳欲聾地安靜\n也沒留下一點痕跡\n如果真的有\n那可能也只是\n我不小心會錯意","excerpt":"他們一個個地走了，離開之前，還不忘貼心的關上門，深怕我懶得起身，燈也一併關上吧，免得太過刺眼，我也不會以為，還有人在，才能安心入睡吧，雖然不知道，明早會不會醒來，不過那都沒關係了，承諾離開的時候總是很","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-19T23:35:42.747Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-19T23:35:42.747Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":8,"tags":["HIDE_THUMBNAIL"],"topics":["創作","文字","心情"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"秋","department":"intimate","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":7},{"id":"514c2569-fd53-4d9d-a415-bf0f88e7329f","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[],"postAvatar":""}